OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FAnticipation in Seoul is sky high as
OL,7,FBTS, one of the world's most
OL,8,Fsuccessful bands in recent history, is
OL,9,Fset to perform together for the first
OL,10,Ftime since October 2022.
OL,12,FSaturday's show in South Korea's
OL,13,Fcapital will mark the end of the
OL,14,Fband's almost four-year hiatus and the
OL,15,Fstart of the their 82-date sold-out
OL,16,Ftour, finally giving fans Permission
OL,17,Fto Dance again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
