OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FThe Arirang World Tour coincides with
OL,7,Fthe release of the K-pop sensation's
OL,8,F10th studio album Arirang, which has
OL,9,Fbeen pre-saved over 5 million times on
OL,10,FSpotify alone.
OL,12,FThe global superstars already hold the
OL,13,Frecord for the most streamed male
OL,14,Fgroup on the platform, with over forty-
OL,15,Ffive billion streams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
