OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774026671
OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FBTS's open-air comeback concert will
OL,7,Ftake place in Gwanghwamun Square,
OL,8,FSeoul, where some 260,000 fans are
OL,9,Fexpected to gather to watch RM, Jin,
OL,10,FSuga, J-hope, Jimin, V and Jungkook
OL,11,Fpreform.
OL,13,FWhile 22,000 of those are ticket-
OL,14,Fholders for the free event, the
OL,15,Fmajority of fans will be watching on
OL,16,Fgiant screens outside.
OL,18,FThe gig will also air on Netflix,
OL,19,Fstreamed live for fans in more than
OL,20,F190 countries across the globe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
