OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FBTS have been on a hiatus since 2022,
OL,7,Fas all seven of the band members were
OL,8,Frequired to complete their military
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FIn South Korea, it is mandatory for
OL,12,Fall able-bodied male citizens,
OL,13,Ftypically between ages 18 and 28, to
OL,14,Fserve in the military for around 18
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,17,FBand member Jin was the first to begin
OL,18,Fhis conscription in 2022, with Suga
OL,19,Ffinishing his service in June last
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
