OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FAll members of BTS have released solo
OL,7,Fmusic during their break from the
OL,8,Fband, however, Arirang is their first
OL,9,Falbum back as a group.
OL,11,FAhead of the album release, band
OL,12,Fmember Jin said: "We gave deep thought
OL,13,Fto our identity ` and how best to
OL,14,Fexpress ourselves authentically `
OL,15,Facross the entirety of our music and
OL,16,Fperformances."
OL,26,@tD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
