OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FHe added: "As an extension of that
OL,7,Fprocess, we also revisited the
OL,8,Fsignificance of our background as a
OL,9,Fgroup comprised entirely of Korean
OL,10,Fmembers."
OL,12,FBTS will be preforming their new album
OL,13,Fas part of their world tour, which
OL,14,Fincludes two July dates at Tottenham
OL,15,FHotspur Stadium.
OL,17,FTickets to the sold-out show cost
OL,18,Fbetween #76 and #477 before fees, with
OL,19,Fhospitality packages upwards of #1,500.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
