OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSome resellers are listening tickets
OL,12,Ffor over three times face value,
OL,13,Falthough Tottenham Hotspur Stadium say
OL,14,Ffans should "only purchase from
OL,15,Fofficial, partnered ticket sellers" to
OL,16,Favoid disappointment.
