OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FBTS's last preformed in the UK in
OL,7,F2019, playing two told-out shows at
OL,8,FWembley Stadium. Tickets for this tour
OL,9,Fwere priced at around #45and#175
OL,10,Fbefore fees.
OL,12,FThe explosion of K-pop in the UK and
OL,13,FUS in recent years
OL,15,FK-pop, once a localised genre, has
OL,16,Fbecome a world-wide phenomenon, moving
OL,17,Finto the mainstream charts in the UK
OL,18,Fand US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
