OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FFirst emerging in the 50s in South
OL,7,FKorea and becoming more popular in the
OL,8,F90s, the genre blends pop, hip-hop,
OL,9,Felectronic dance music and R&B with
OL,10,Ftraditional Korean music.
OL,12,FThe music is often accompanied by
OL,13,Fsleek choreography and cohesive
OL,14,Ffashion choices, with bands such as
OL,15,FBTS, BLACKPINK and Stray Kids building
OL,16,Fhuge followings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
