OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FROSE, one quarter of BLACKPINK won
OL,7,FInternational Song of the Year at the
OL,8,FBRIT Awards this year for her
OL,9,Fcollaboration with pop star Bruno
OL,10,FMars, APT
OL,12,FK-pop has also impacted film, with
OL,13,FNetflix's animated film KPop Demon
OL,14,FHunters became the platform's most
OL,15,Fstreamed film of all time.
OL,17,FThe fantasy musical, which won two
OL,18,FOscars at this year's Academy Awards,
OL,19,Fis about a fictional K-pop girl group
OL,20,Fand features catchy songs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
