OL,3,CK-pop mega stars BTS are back after
OL,4,Cfour-year hiatus
OL,6,FAs well as having strong global
OL,7,Finfluence over film and music, the
OL,8,Fgenre has also had a significant
OL,9,Fimpact on tourism and the economy,
OL,10,Fboth in South Korea and here in the UK.
OL,12,FAccording to government figures, 1.36
OL,13,Fmillion international travellers
OL,14,Fvisited Seoul in July 2025 alone,
OL,15,Fshowing a 23.1% rise from 2024.
OL,17,FReports estimate that spending linked
OL,18,Fto Korean culture in the UK could be
OL,19,Fadding #3.5 billion to the UK economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
